---

<Layout
  tags={tags}
  icon="beach"
  title="About Me"
  description={description}
  pubDate={new Date("2 Aug 2026")}
  heroImage="/src/assets/me.jpeg"
>
  <!-- <div class="portrait">
    <img src="/src/assets/me.jpeg" alt="Huiyang Wang" />
  </div> -->

  <div class="about-content">
    <h1>Huiyang Wang (Wystan Wang)</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">Sound Artist · Creative Technologist · Poet</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Biography</h2>

    <p>
      I am a poet, sound artist, and backend software engineer working across
      sound art, algorithmic art.
    </p>

    <p>
      Originally trained as a software engineer, I later completed an MSc in
      Sound Design at the University of Edinburgh. My practice explores
      ecological processes, non-human agency, computational aesthetics, and
      interaction through code, sound, and installation.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>Research Interests</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Sound Art</li>
      <li>Ecological Sound Art</li>
      <li>Creative Coding</li>
      <li>Audio Programming</li>
      <li>Max/MSP</li>
      <li>Generative Systems</li>
      <li>Algorithmic Composition</li>
      <li>Interactive Installation</li>
      <li>Physical Computing</li>
      <li>Artificial Life</li>
      <li>Posthumanism</li>
    </ul>

    <hr />
    <h2>Education</h2>

    <p>
      <strong>MSc Sound Design</strong><br />
      The University of Edinburgh
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Email<br />
      <a href="mailto: wanghuiyang5050@gmail.com"> wanghuiyang5050@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    <p>
      GitHub<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/GrayOxygen">
        https://github.com/GrayOxygen
      </a>
    </p> 
    <p>
      SoundCloud<br />
      <a href="https://soundcloud.com/krazymango">
        https://soundcloud.com/krazymango
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
